message.content: Ndĩwehe, ngunjiri yaku kũtuma ũkumbũkire cia kũrĩa cia wendo nĩ thĩinĩ. Ndĩkũhonete kũmenya ngũcio ũcio na kũhongwo ciothe cia kũrĩa cia wendo cia kamba. Ndĩkũrĩra na kũkuhe rĩu rĩa kũrĩa cia wendo ciothe cia kamba waku, na nginya ndĩkũrĩra kũhongwo ciothe cia kũrĩa cia wendo cia kamba waku.
